{"word":"Philip","slug":"philip","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Philip</b> - <b>(a) The Apostle</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=10&verse=3'>Mat 10:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=1&verse=43'>Joh 1:43</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=6&verse=5'>Joh 6:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=12&verse=21'>Joh 12:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=14&verse=8'>Joh 14:8</a><p/>-- A Personal Worker<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=1&verse=45'>Joh 1:45</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=12&verse=21'>Joh 12:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=12&verse=22'>Joh 12:22</a><p/>-- Tested by Christ<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=6&verse=5'>Joh 6:5</a><p/>-- Slow to apprehend Truth<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=14&verse=8'>Joh 14:8</a><p/><b>(b) \"The Evangelistic Deacon\"</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=6&verse=5'>Ac 6:5</a><p/>-- Broadminded<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=8&verse=5'>Ac 8:5</a><p/>-- Led of the \"Spirit\"<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=8&verse=26'>Ac 8:26</a><p/>-- Preacher of the \"Word\"<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=8&verse=34'>Ac 8:34</a><p/>-- Had a godly household<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=21&verse=8'>Ac 21:8</a><p/><b>(c) The Brother of Herod</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=14&verse=3'>Mat 14:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=6&verse=17'>Mar 6:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=3&verse=1'>Luk 3:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=3&verse=19'>Luk 3:19</a><p/><b>--SEE</b> Herods, HERODS OF THE NEW TESTAMENT, THE"}]}